Ties, therefore, until today. "We look forward to developments with reasonable hope that the truth can finally emerge," Stasi's lawyers hope. "We have known from tg1, we have nothing to say"> is the comment of Giuseppe Poggi and Rita Preda, whose composed sobriety in these years of pain has always been a certainty even in the most turbulent days of the media doga, and it is also now that it questioned a truth that seemed now unwavering.
